{"type": "article", "id": 16689, "title": "Yeezy Boost 350 手机壳", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-28T06:14:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060614080265pKyw1qbA4VFsRO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是由 KickPoster 推出的手机壳，适合 iPhone 4 到 6s 所有型号。它直接将 adidas 在今年 6 月份发布的 Yeezy Boost 350 的花纹复制到鞋面上，黑灰两款虎纹自然而霸气，放在手机壳上也是酷炫的装饰。<span>从另一种角度来看，它也揭示了运动鞋在同一个版型里变化配色的现状，那就不如直接将配色做成其他的产品。</span>售价 20 英镑，<a href=\"http://kickposters.bigcartel.com/product/pre-order-br-yzy-phone-cases-br\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144003EWcNboU7upRmH1wr.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144004LKYvQm09N1P3IMJG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144005LlsfOMj0ptoVBKXu.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"718\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}